			"entries": [
				"You conjure a protective shelter. A simple, camouflaged, stationary dome of magical energy with a 10-foot Emanation. The shelter provides cover from the elements, masking its interior from wind, rain, and snow. The shelter blends with the surroundings, granting disadvantage to Perception checks made by creatures outside the dome to detect it.",
				"All creatures, objects, and spells can move through it freely."
			],
