				"You conjure a radiant burst of arcane energy and launch it at one creature or object within range. Make a ranged spell attack against the target. On a hit, the target takes {@damage 1d4} Radiant damage.",
				"If the target is {@status Concentration|XPHB|Concentrating} on a spell, the Constitution saving throw DC to maintain {@status Concentration|XPHB} is 10 + the amount of Radiant damage dealt by this spell."
