			"entries": [
				"You deploy a swarm of extremely small flying automatons at a point within range. The swarm takes up a 10-foot diameter Sphere, which can overlap with the space of creatures. ",
				"When you create the swarm and as a Bonus Action on your subsequent turns, you can command it to move up to 30 feet and perform one of the following actions:",
				{
