			"entries": [
				"A lane of cracks forms along the ground in a 60-foot long, 15-foot wide line in a direction you choose. From these cracks, a wave of sharp, black, skeletal limbs flail about, ripping through any creature within the area.",
				"A creature within the area must make a Constitution saving throw. On a failure, the creature takes {@damage 7d6} Necrotic damage, and its Maximum Hit Points are reduced by {@dice 1d8} until the creature completes a Long Rest. On a success, the creature takes half damage and its Maximum Hit Points are not reduced.",
				"Afterwards, the cracks seal closed."
