			"entries": [
				"You call forth the essence of a mindless blob. It manifests in an unoccupied space that you can see within range and uses the {@creature Ooze Spirit|CoopersCompendiumofComplexities} stat block. When you cast the spell, choose a form: Gelatinous Cube, Jelly, Oblex, or Oozebleck. The creature resembles an amorphous ooze, with coloration of your choosing, and characteristics marked by the chosen form. The creature disappears when it drops to 0 {@variantrule Hit Points|XPHB} or when the spell ends.",
				"The creature is an ally to you and your allies. In combat, the creature shares your Initiative count, but it takes its turn immediately after yours. It obeys your verbal commands (no action required by you). If you don't issue any, it takes the {@action Dodge|XPHB} action and uses its movement to avoid danger."
