			"entries": [
				"You launch a strong wind full of {@condition burning|MonstersOfDrakkenheim} ash in a 5-foot-wide, 60-foot-long Line. Each creature in the Line makes a Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, a creature takes {@damage 5d10} Fire damage and has the {@condition Blinded|XPHB} condition until the start of your next turn. On a successful save, it takes half as much damage only.",
				"Each creature in the Line must also succeed on a Strength saving throw or be pushed 20 feet away from you in a direction following the Line.",
				"The gale also disperses gas or vapor, and has a 50 percent chance to light candles and similar unprotected flames in the area.",
				"Until the spell ends, you can take a Magic action to create a new Line of cinders."
