			"entries": [
				"You conjure the smothering gloom of the dark side of Aureban. Upon casting this spell, everywhere within a 1-mile Radius centered on you becomes shrouded in {@variantrule darkness|XPHB}, as if there were no sun.",
				"All creatures, items, spells, features, etc. within this area that are effected by {@variantrule darkness|XPHB} or nighttime may function as if it were night for the duration of the spell."
