						"{@actSave dex} {@dc 14}. Each creature in a 30-foot Cone from the boilwurm as it regurgitates its digestive system in a web of {@condition burning|MonstersOfDrakkenheim} insides before rapidly sucking its caught prey back into its maw. {@actSaveFail} 21 ({@damage 6d6}) Fire damage and the target is Swallowed by the boilwurm. {@actSaveSuccess} Half damage."
					]
				}
			],
			"actionTags": [
				"Multiattack",
				"Swallow"
			],
			"conditionInflict": [
				"grappled"
			],
			"miscTags": [
				"RCH"
			],
			"bonus": [
				{
					"name": "Swallow",
					"entries": [
						"The boilwurm swallows a Medium or smaller creature it is grappling. While swallowed, the target isn’t {@condition Grappled|XPHB} but has the {@condition Blinded|XPHB} and {@condition Restrained|XPHB} conditions, and it has Full Cover against attacks and other effects outside the boilwurm. In addition, the target takes 14 ({@damage 4d6}) Fire damage and 14 ({@damage 4d6}) Acid damage at the end of each of the boilwurm’s turns. If the boilwurm dies, a swallowed creature is no longer Restained and can escape from the corpse using 5 feet of movement, exiting with the {@condition Prone|XPHB} condition."
					]
				}
			],
			"fluff": {
				"entries": [
					"Although the exact origins of how the boilwurm made it to Aureban is unclear, it is widely believed that it arrived from the Elemental Plane of Fire during the Great Confluence.",
					"Boilwurms are considered one of the few invasive creatures in Aureban, not having any connection to any ecosystem on the planet, and thriving by simply consuming anything and everything they can.",
					"Designed to survive the heat of the Elemental Plane of Fire, boilwurms have molten insides. Adapting to the relatively temperate climate of the Sunspot Desert, boilwurms have developed a unique method of digestion; by regurgitating its digestive organs with such velocity that it coats and captures its prey, before sucking its organs back, having swallowed its prey in the process and already beginning digestion."
				]
			},
			"environment": [
				"desert",
				"plane of fire"
			],
			"damageTags": [
				"A",
				"F",
				"P"
			],
			"savingThrowForced": [
				"dexterity"
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Chupacabra",
			"size": [
				"M"
			],
			"type": "monstrosity",
