					]
				},
				{
					"name": "Wingbeat Gale",
					"entries": [
						"The roc makes a {@dc 20} Strength check. On a success, it can fly up to 40 feet, then each creature in a 40-foot Emanation from it must make a {@dc 17} Strength saving throw. On a failure, a creature has the {@condition Prone|XPHB} condition.",
