			"fluff": {
				"entries": [
					"The origin of the sasquatch is unclear, and many do not believe it exists. Those that do, however, report a hulking, hairy, bipedal beast of a creature that, at a distance, blends in with the trees. Unnervingly stealthy for its size, and brutal in its attacks, the sasquatch is rumored to have claimed the lives of many an explorer."
