					"entries": [
						"{@atkr m} {@hit 7} to hit, reach 5 ft., one target {@h}11 ({@damage 2d6 + 4}) Slashing damage."
					]
				},
				{
					"name": "Gore",
					"entries": [
						"{@atkr m} {@hit 7} to hit, reach 5 ft., one target {@h}8 ({@damage 1d8 + 4}) Piercing damage. If the target is a Medium or smaller creature and the sheepsquatch moved at least 20 feet straight towards the target immediately before the hit, the target takes an extra 9 ({@damage 2d8}) Piercing damage and has the {@condition Prone|XPHB} condition."
					]
				},
				{
					"name": "Putrid Spray {@recharge 5}",
					"entries": [
						"{@actSave con} {@dc 14}, each creature in a 15-foot Cone originating from the sheepsquatch. {@actSaveFail} 18 ({@dice 4d8}) Acid and 18 ({@damage 4d8}) Poison damage, and the target has the Corroded condition.",
						"A Corroded creature or object has a -1 penalty to its AC. As an Action, a creature can neutralize the corrosion by going {@condition Prone|XPHB} and rolling on the ground. The corrosion is also neutralized when a creature is doused with water."
					]
