			"actionTags": [
				"Multiattack"
			],
			"miscTags": [
				"MA"
			],
			"fluff": {
				"entries": [
					"The sheepsquatch is a mutated monstrosity. It appears like a monstrous goat which stands on its hind legs, has large twisting horns, and a distinctive goat skull which is visible under its thin facial skin. The sheepsquatch is as large as a bear and about as strong. Its skin is covered in rashes and boils, and it emits a foul odor.",
					"Sheepsquatchs are mutants, typically the result of rampant arcane energy’s effect on unfortunate sheep. They can be created on purpose or be the byproduct of untrained spellcasters, mages drawing on too much energy, or magical artifacts gone awry.",
					"These creatures are omnivores and eat pretty much anything they can get a hold of. They are also highly territorial and aggressive, so often come into conflict with native wildlife. Sheepsquatchs prefer to be isolated, but they will venture into nearby settlements to feed on leftovers, livestock, and unsuspecting people."
				]
			},
